<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN"><head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>百度竞价落地页URL匹配工具</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0d1117;
    --bg-card: #161b22;
    --bg-input: #0d1117;
    --bg-hover: #1f2630;
    --bg-row-alt: #11161d;
    --border: #30363d;
    --border-light: #21262d;
    --text: #e6edf3;
    --text-muted: #8b949e;
    --text-dim: #6e7681;
    --primary: #2f81f7;
    --primary-hover: #1f6feb;
    --primary-dim: #0d2d5e;
    --success: #3fb950;
    --success-dim: #1a3a26;
    --danger: #f85149;
    --danger-dim: #3a1a1c;
    --warning: #d29922;
    --warning-dim: #3a2e14;
    --accent: #a371f7;
    --accent-dim: #2a1f4a;
    --radius: 8px;
    --shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* 顶部栏 */
  .topbar {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #161b22 0%, #0d1117 100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 14px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }
  .topbar-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .logo {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
  }
  .topbar h1 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; }
  .topbar h1 small { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400; margin-left: 8px; }
  .topbar-right { display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: center; }

  /* 按钮 */
  .btn {
    padding: 7px 14px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    color: var(--text);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 13px;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .btn:hover { background: var(--bg-hover); border-color: var(--text-muted); }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--primary); border-color: var(--primary); color: #fff; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-hover); border-color: var(--primary-hover); }
  .btn-success { background: var(--success-dim); border-color: var(--success); color: var(--success); }
  .btn-success:hover { background: var(--success); color: #fff; }
  .btn-danger { background: transparent; border-color: var(--danger); color: var(--danger); }
  .btn-danger:hover { background: var(--danger); color: #fff; }
  .btn-sm { padding: 4px 10px; font-size: 12px; }
  .btn-icon { padding: 6px 8px; }

  /* Tab */
  .tabs {
    display: flex;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 24px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 65px;
    z-index: 90;
  }
  .tab {
    padding: 12px 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .tab:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .tab.active { color: var(--primary); border-bottom-color: var(--primary); font-weight: 500; }
  .tab-badge {
    background: var(--primary-dim);
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 1px 7px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    min-width: 18px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* 主容器 */
  .container { padding: 24px; max-width: 1600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .tab-content { display: none; }
  .tab-content.active { display: block; }

  /* 卡片 */
  .card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card-header {
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: var(--bg-row-alt);
  }
  .card-header h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .card-header .desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }
  .card-body { padding: 18px; }

  /* 表单元素 */
  label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  input[type="text"], input[type="url"], textarea, select {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--bg-input);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: inherit;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  input:focus, textarea:focus, select:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(47,129,247,0.15);
  }
  textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 180px; line-height: 1.6; font-family: "Consolas", "Courier New", monospace; }
  select { cursor: pointer; }

  .form-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .form-group { flex: 1; min-width: 160px; }
  .form-group label { margin-bottom: 5px; }

  /* 单选/复选 */
  .radio-group, .check-group { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
  .radio-group label, .check-group label {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    color: var(--text); font-size: 13px; margin: 0; cursor: pointer;
  }
  input[type="radio"], input[type="checkbox"] { accent-color: var(--primary); cursor: pointer; }

  /* 表格 */
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; max-height: 520px; overflow-y: auto; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
  thead { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10; background: var(--bg-row-alt); }
  th {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  td {
    padding: 9px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  tbody tr:hover { background: var(--bg-hover); }
  tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: var(--bg-row-alt); }
  tbody tr:nth-child(even):hover { background: var(--bg-hover); }
  .url-cell { color: var(--accent); word-break: break-all; font-family: "Consolas", monospace; font-size: 12px; }
  .url-cell:hover { text-decoration: underline; cursor: pointer; }

  /* 状态标签 */
  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .tag-success { background: var(--success-dim); color: var(--success); }
  .tag-danger { background: var(--danger-dim); color: var(--danger); }
  .tag-warning { background: var(--warning-dim); color: var(--warning); }
  .tag-primary { background: var(--primary-dim); color: var(--primary); }
  .tag-accent { background: var(--accent-dim); color: var(--accent); }
  .tag-muted { background: var(--bg-hover); color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* 统计条 */
  .stats-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    background: var(--bg-row-alt);
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .stat-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .stat-num { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* 操作区 */
  .action-bar { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 14px; align-items: center; }
  .action-bar .spacer { flex: 1; }

  /* 提示 */
  .alert {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-size: 13px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .alert-info { background: var(--primary-dim); border: 1px solid var(--primary); color: #a8c7fa; }
  .alert-warning { background: var(--warning-dim); border: 1px solid var(--warning); color: #e3b341; }
  .alert-success { background: var(--success-dim); border: 1px solid var(--success); color: #56d364; }

  /* 代码块 */
  code, .mono { font-family: "Consolas", "Courier New", monospace; background: var(--bg-input); padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent); }
  pre { background: var(--bg-input); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; overflow-x: auto; font-family: "Consolas", monospace; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* 开关 */
  .switch { position: relative; display: inline-block; width: 38px; height: 22px; }
  .switch input { opacity: 0; width: 0; height: 0; }
  .slider {
    position: absolute; cursor: pointer; inset: 0;
    background: var(--border); border-radius: 22px; transition: 0.2s;
  }
  .slider:before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; height: 16px; width: 16px;
    left: 3px; bottom: 3px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50%; transition: 0.2s;
  }
  .switch input:checked + .slider { background: var(--success); }
  .switch input:checked + .slider:before { transform: translateX(16px); }

  /* 拖拽手柄 */
  .drag-handle { cursor: grab; color: var(--text-dim); user-select: none; padding: 0 4px; }
  .drag-handle:active { cursor: grabbing; }
  .drag-handle:hover { color: var(--text-muted); }
  tr.dragging { opacity: 0.4; }
  tr.drag-over { border-top: 2px solid var(--primary); }

  /* Toast */
  #toast {
    position: fixed; bottom: 30px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text); padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); z-index: 9999;
    display: none; font-size: 14px; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  }
  #toast.show { display: flex; animation: slideUp 0.3s; }
  @keyframes slideUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translate(-50%, 20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%, 0); } }

  /* 空状态 */
  .empty-state { text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .empty-state .icon { font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 12px; opacity: 0.5; }

  /* 说明文档 */
  .doc-section { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .doc-section h4 { color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .doc-section ul { margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .doc-section li { margin-bottom: 6px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .doc-section table { margin: 10px 0; }
  .doc-section td:first-child { white-space: nowrap; color: var(--accent); font-family: monospace; }

  .footer-note { text-align: center; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 12px; padding: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light); margin-top: 30px; }

  /* 滚动条 */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 10px; height: 10px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); border-radius: 5px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--text-muted); }

  .input-format-hint {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-top: 6px;
    padding: 8px 12px; background: var(--bg-input); border-radius: 6px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
  }
  .hidden { display: none !important; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- 顶部栏 -->
<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-left">
    <div class="logo">U</div>
    <h1>百度竞价落地页URL匹配工具 <small>本地离线 · 双击即用</small></h1>
  </div>
  <div class="topbar-right">
    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-success" onclick="saveToHtmlFile()" title="把当前数据写回HTML文件，复制到任何电脑都是最新版" id="btnSaveHtml" style="">💾 保存到文件</button>
    <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="exportConfig()">导出规则</button>
    <label class="btn btn-sm" style="cursor:pointer;">
      导入规则
      <input type="file" accept=".json" style="display:none;" onchange="importConfig(event)">
    </label>
    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-danger" onclick="clearAllData()">清空数据</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Tab 导航 -->
<div class="tabs">
  <div class="tab" data-tab="match" onclick="switchTab('match')">匹配执行</div>
  <div class="tab active" data-tab="rules" onclick="switchTab('rules')">规则配置 <span class="tab-badge" id="rules-count">126</span></div>
  <div class="tab" data-tab="domains" onclick="switchTab('domains')">域名管理 <span class="tab-badge" id="domains-count">5</span></div>
  <div class="tab" data-tab="docs" onclick="switchTab('docs')">使用说明</div>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <!-- ============ 匹配执行 Tab ============ -->
  <div class="tab-content" id="tab-match">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <h3>输入关键词</h3>
          <div class="desc">从 Excel 复制粘贴即可，支持 Tab 分隔的多列</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group" style="flex:0 0 auto;">
            <label>输入格式</label>
            <div class="radio-group" onchange="updateInputHint()">
              <label><input type="radio" name="inputFormat" value="keyword" checked=""> 仅关键词</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="inputFormat" value="pu"> 计划 + 单元 + 关键词</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="inputFormat" value="full"> 计划+单元+关键词+类别</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="input-format-hint" id="inputHint">每行一个关键词。示例：<br><span class="mono">奉贤区产业园厂房租赁</span><br><span class="mono">卢湾工业园厂房</span></div>
        <div style="margin-top:12px;">
          <label>粘贴内容（支持从 Excel 直接复制，Tab 分隔列）</label>
          <textarea id="inputArea" placeholder="在此粘贴关键词，每行一个或按选定格式粘贴..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="action-bar">
          <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="runMatch()">执行匹配</button>
          <button class="btn" onclick="loadSampleInput()">载入示例</button>
          <button class="btn" onclick="document.getElementById('inputArea').value=''; clearResults();">清空输入</button>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <span style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:12px;">匹配规则按优先级从上到下，命中即停止</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" id="resultCard">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <h3>匹配结果</h3>
          <div class="desc">点击 URL 可复制单个 · 复制全部可直接粘贴回 Excel</div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;">
          <button class="btn btn-sm btn-success" onclick="copyAllResults()">复制全部结果</button>
          <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="exportResults()">导出 CSV</button>
          <button class="btn btn-sm btn-danger" onclick="copyUnmatched()">仅复制未匹配</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="stats-bar">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-num" id="stat-total">2</span>
            <span class="stat-label">总条数</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-num" style="color:var(--success)" id="stat-matched">2</span>
            <span class="stat-label">已匹配</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-num" style="color:var(--danger)" id="stat-unmatched">0</span>
            <span class="stat-label">未匹配</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-num" style="color:var(--warning)" id="stat-default">0</span>
            <span class="stat-label">走默认URL</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>#</th>
                <th>计划</th>
                <th>单元</th>
                <th>关键词</th>
                <th>类别</th>
                <th>命中规则</th>
                <th>匹配类型</th>
                <th>最终URL</th>
                <th>状态</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id="resultBody"><tr><td>1</td><td></td><td></td><td>苏州高新区</td><td></td><td><span class="tag tag-muted">AI页面-苏州高新区</span></td><td><span class="tag tag-primary">关键词包含</span></td><td class="url-cell" onclick="copyText(this.textContent)" title="点击复制">https://qgqydoo.xuannaer.com.cn/chouhua/szgxq/?utm_source=SEM-baidu-PC&amp;utm_medium=PC</td><td><span class="tag tag-success">已匹配</span></td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td></td><td></td><td>东升科技园</td><td></td><td><span class="tag tag-muted">东升科技园</span></td><td><span class="tag tag-primary">关键词包含</span></td><td class="url-cell" onclick="copyText(this.textContent)" title="点击复制">https://qgyaunqu.zhaoshang.net/yuanqu/park/zgcdskjy?utm_source=SEM-baidu-PC&amp;utm_medium=PC</td><td><span class="tag tag-success">已匹配</span></td></tr></tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ============ 规则配置 Tab ============ -->
  <div class="tab-content active" id="tab-rules">

    <!-- 批量粘贴建规则 -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <h3>批量粘贴建规则</h3>
          <div class="desc">从 Excel 复制粘贴即可批量生成规则 · 每行一条 · Tab 分隔列</div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-sm" onclick="toggleBatchPaste()">展开/收起</button>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body hidden" id="batchPasteCard">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group" style="flex:0 0 auto;">
            <label>粘贴格式</label>
            <div class="radio-group" onchange="updateBatchPasteHint()">
              <label><input type="radio" name="batchFormat" value="puu" checked=""> 计划|||单元 → URL</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="batchFormat" value="uu"> 单元 → URL</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="batchFormat" value="custom"> 自定义列</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="input-format-hint" id="batchPasteHint">三列 Tab 分隔：<b>计划名</b> <b>单元名</b> <b>完整URL</b>。匹配类型自动设为「计划+单元」，value格式：<code>计划|||单元</code>。<br>示例：<span class="mono">上海-大词&nbsp;&nbsp;园区&nbsp;&nbsp;https://sh.xuannaer.com.cn/yuanqu/list/?utm_source=SEM-baidu-PC</span></div>
        <div style="margin-top:12px;">
          <label>粘贴内容（每行一条规则）</label>
          <textarea id="batchPasteArea" placeholder="在此粘贴，每行一条规则，Tab 分隔列..." style="min-height:140px;"></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="action-bar">
          <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="batchPasteCreate()">生成规则</button>
          <button class="btn" onclick="document.getElementById('batchPasteArea').value='';">清空</button>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <span style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:12px;" id="batchPasteCount">0 行</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 规则列表 -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div>
          <h3>匹配规则</h3>
          <div class="desc">优先级从上到下 · 拖拽行可调整顺序 · 命中第一条后停止 · 勾选可批量操作</div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <select id="ruleRegionFilter" style="padding:5px 10px;font-size:12px;" onchange="renderRules()"><option value="">全部地域</option><option value="上海">上海</option><option value="北京">北京</option><option value="天津">天津</option><option value="安徽" selected="">安徽</option><option value="山东">山东</option><option value="广东">广东</option><option value="新疆">新疆</option><option value="江苏">江苏</option><option value="浙江">浙江</option><option value="湖南">湖南</option></select>
          <input type="text" id="ruleSearch" placeholder="搜索规则..." style="width:180px;padding:5px 10px;font-size:12px;" oninput="renderRules()">
          <button class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" onclick="addRule()">+ 添加规则</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 批量操作栏 -->
      <div id="batchBar" style="background: var(--primary-dim); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--primary); padding: 8px 18px; display: none; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
